name: Terra Nova Digital Ambassador
description:
50% of proceeds will be donated to the wereachfoundation.org for Haiti's earthquake victims.

This photo is from the short film "Lifestyle of a new age low key Investor" Cameo appearance by promoter "Cheeks." Digital ambassadors volunteer their time to bring awareness to Haiti's earthquake victims. The members of this cast are comprised of gold, crypto, and real estate investors. Our cast was strategically assembled to showcase some of Miami's local businesses and professionals. Also local business owners make cameo appearances and product placements. The Blue Lagoon Redland Farm in Homestead, Florida, location was used in the film storyline, as an off-grid private meet up, where new age low key investors network.

Executive producer and music produced by 
J. Classic-Maestro

Creative Director Maicol Diaz
